WEBVTT

00:00.527 --> 00:03.711
The word THIS tells us about something close.

00:05.398 --> 00:07.093
This is an animal.

00:08.824 --> 00:10.185
This is a place.

00:11.871 --> 00:13.785
This place is a house.

00:15.449 --> 00:17.040
This toy is a robot.

00:18.593 --> 00:22.474
The word THAT tells us about something far away.

00:24.425 --> 00:26.052
That is an animal.

00:27.877 --> 00:30.112
That place is a mountain.

00:31.807 --> 00:33.008
That is a tree.

00:34.779 --> 00:36.423
That man is a teacher.

